      "name": "Linked Data",
      "abstract": "Linked Data gives public knowledge systems a way to make entities, pages, references and datasets interoperable across sites and software systems.",
      "description": "Linked Data is a web publishing approach that identifies things with stable URIs and connects them through machine-readable statements.",
